Drain @sliced mushrooms {1 can}
Mix @Campbell’s French Onion{2 cans}, @Campbell’s Beef Consommé{2 cans}, @butter{1 stick}, @rice, non-instant{2 cups} in a #cake pan (13x9){} or foil pan.
Bake at 375°F for an ~{hour or so}: the liquid should all be absorbed.

